	<div class="contentDetailNews">
	<h5>Insight Into Diversity magazine recognizes contributions of Maja Matarić and Urbashi Mitra</h5>
<div class="noprint" align="right">
 <table align="right" cellpadding="5" cellspacing="0">
        <tr>
          <td valign="top">
